Andy Murray's Get Inspired Q&amp;A
Tennis star Andy Murray has revealed his thoughts on everything from sandwiches, shoes, whether he might coach one day, and the possibility of starting a family.The Wimbledon champion took part in a live BBC question and answer session with school pupils from around the UK.The event, hosted by Sue Barker, was broadcast from Wallace High School in Stirling on Wednesday 23 April 2014.*Live coverage has ended. The email address mentioned is no longer valid.For information on how to get started in tennis and find local events to you, check out ourGet Inspired tennis pages.